data.description: Nestled in the desired community Trails of Shaker Run, this beautifully maintained and updated home offers 5 bedrooms, 3 full bathrooms, a brand new roof & water heater in 2023! Enjoy the swimming, walking trails, and other amenities close by that this community as to offer. Upstairs, you'll find a spacious loft suited perfectly for a game room or additional living area.  The five bedrooms offer lots of space, with three of them including walk-in closets. The office could serve as an in-law suite to friends and family or a potential sixth bedroom. Other updates include new AC unit and LV flooring in 2020, unfinished basement has plumbing hookups for a potential full bathroom. With charming built-ins to various accent pieces throughout, this is the perfect place to call   home just in time for the holidays!    Agent owned
